eas_text: A civil authority has issued A CHILD ABDUCTION EMERGENCY for the following counties or areas: Washington; at 09:09 PM ON DEC 12, 2025 Effective until 10:09 PM. Message from WSLF/CAP.
extra_text: The Washington State Patrol on behalf of the Burien Police Department has issued an Amber Alert for a 5 year old and 5 month old. Victims are a 5 year old Female named Harmoni Collins that is 3 Foot 10 Inches tall, weighs 53 lbs, has brown hair, brown eyes wearing hoodie, jeans, black/white Nike shoes and a 5 months old Male Donte Petway that 2 Foot 3 Inches tall, weights 17 lbs, has brown hair, brown eyes. They were last seen on 12-12-2025 12:00. They are in the company of Tilla Castillo, a 31 year old Female,  who is 5 Foot 7 Inches, weighing 184 lbs with brown hair, brown eyes, wearing gray adidas shoes.  They may be traveling in a Black 1997 Toyota Camry Washington License C S G 6 2 6 3. If you have information, please call 9 1 1.
